data.description: In the heart of Alamo Ranch. Fast commute to 1604 or 151.  Under 1 mi to Alamo Ranch HEB, CVS and Walgreens, 3 m from Alamo Ranch Marketplace. Save with NO CITY TAXES!  Brick, Arched Windows, Front Porch. High Ceilings. 5 bdrm, 3 baths + half bath downstairs. Extra tall 2 car garage. New roof 9/2023. New A/C and heat 2019 has transferable warranty for parts and labor through 2029. SELLER FINANCING available at $440,000 purchase price, 7.5% interest, 30 year amortization, 20% down, no balloon payment. USDA $0 down program.    A wall of windows through the open living area, views the backyard with mature tree, corner to corner covered patio for all your evenings and parties. Stainless steel appliances and pendant lighting accent endless white cabinets in the granite kitchen located between the breakfast room and a gorgeous dining room with arched double windows.     Tons of tile and vinyl flooring. Carpet only in some closets. Big laundry room with a window. Powder room with gorgeous vanity.     Gigantic downstairs main suite with glamorous, full bay window and ensuite bath.  Garden tub + a shower, double vanity, enclosed WC, and giant walk-in closet.    Upstairs are 2 bedrooms, separated by a Jack and Jill bath and 2 additional bedrooms +  bath 3 upstairs. All bedrooms have walk-in closets, Giant game room is big enough for a full-size pool table + players!    Mature Landscaping. Flat backyard. N'hood pool, courts & park a couple of blocks away. Great NISD  Schools. Shopping & Dining. Close to Medical Services and Hospitals. Lackland AFB, Casa Blanca Theaters and Sea World.
